'''Ernesto Tornquist Provincial Park''' ({{lang-es|Parque Provincial Ernesto Tornquist}}) is a [[List of Provincial Parks of Buenos Aires|provincial protected area]] in the south of [[Buenos Aires Province]], mid-eastern [[Argentina]]. Established on 23 April 1958,<ref name=decree1/> it covers a small area of the [[Sierra de la Ventana (mountains)|Ventania System]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.welcomeargentina.com/sierradelaventana/ernesto-tornquist-provincial-park.html|title=Ernesto Tornquist Provincial Park|publisher=Welcome Argentina|date=|accessdate=7 September 2012}}</ref>

