'''Meng-p'o''' is the easternmost of the "[[Brass Knuckles (Pluto)|Brass Knuckles]]", a series of equatorial dark regions on [[Pluto]]. Meng-p'o straddles the zero meridian, directly under Pluto's tidally locked moon [[Charon (moon)|Charon]] and just west of the tail of the "Whale", [[Cthulhu Macula]]. It is named after [[Meng Po]] {{IPAc-cmn|m|eng|4|p|o|2}}, the Chinese underworld deity of forgetfulness.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Chang|first1=Kenneth|title=NASA’s New Horizons Spacecraft Completes Flyby of Pluto|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/15/science/space/nasa-new-horizons-spacecraft-reaches-pluto.html|publisher=[[The New York Times]]|accessdate=14 July 2015|date=14 July 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Rogers|first1=Adam|title=The New, Nerdy Mythology of Pluto's Place Names|url=https://www.wired.com/2015/07/new-nerdy-mythology-plutos-place-names/|publisher=Wired|accessdate=14 July 2015|date=14 July 2015}}</ref>
